# Examples where output should be empty (nothing):
# - Only source code/config files (.py, .js, .java, .go, .cpp, .h, .md, .txt, .json, .yml, .yaml, .toml, .cfg, .ini, etc.)
# - Only HTML, CSS, JS source files
# - Only manifest.json, sw.js, or similar config/policy files

